Company Profile:Since May 2011, iLoveDeals.SG has been a deal sites aggregating platform which provides users the convenience of finding the best deals in Singapore.Along with our deal site partners, we intend to bring out the best, fastest and easiest way to make our users closer to their enjoyable shopping experience in their fingertips.We foresee to provide a more user-friendly experience in your online shopping through collecting multiple deal sites into one stop deal sites which won’t make you feel tired in searching for multiple deal sites just to get your favorite deals!We have been one of the Top Singapore E-Commerce Site since May 2011 and has been one of the fast growing E-Commerce Site with continuous growing potential.Our site provides comprehensive high quality traffic solution all range of E-Commerce Site, Merchants & more.We focus mostly on Group Buying Deals, Coupons, Products, Services & more.Candidate open to wide opportunity to learn more about E-Commerce, Group Buying Deals, Coupons, Products, Services & more!
Job Description: Attend to customer enquiries and handle customer feedback/complaints if needed Manage warehouse inventory (e.g. receiving stocks, no./SKU count, storage, outgoing stocks) Packaging of products to be delivered to customersAssist customer walk-ins to collect their purchased productsManage all paperwork related to the flow of products from receiving point to sending pointUse the knowledge and experience gained to improve on ILOVEDEALS's logistical process flowAny other ad-hoc tasks and assignments as requiredJob Requirements Interest in the daily deals/group buying industry/ecommerce in general Interested to work in a start-up environment Good communication, writing and telephone skills Proficient in the use of Internet/MS Office Able to work independently as well as in a teamAbility to multi-task, work under pressure and meet deadlinesGood attitude and customer skills Enthusiasm and a sense of ownership
